videos.description: After a scramble for the offensive rebound, Reid Travis throws down a 2-handed dunk for the Wildcats.
videos.headline: Scramble for a rebound leads to a Kentucky Dunk

videos.description: PJ Washington fires a 3-pointer that hits the back iron and rolls in to give Kentucky the lead over UNC Greensboro.
videos.headline: PJ Washington made Three Point Jumper. Kentucky's Washington makes weird 3-pointer off the back iron

videos.description: Kentucky's Keldon Johnson goes after a rebound and appears to hurt his left ankle, causing him to leave the game.
videos.headline: Kentucky freshman Johnson leaves with injury

videos.description: Kentucky's Reid Travis flies down the lane and slams down a dunk.
videos.headline: Reid Travis flies down the lane for a dunk
